          "trait_date": "2023-09-24T09:37:15.4778215Z",
          "locale_text": "“怎么？你没别的问题要问了？”",
          "speaker": "Quetza-al_Winterscale",
          "speaker_gender": "Male"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "locale": "frFR",
      "text": "« Comment ? Vous n'avez plus de questions ? »",
